text: Saad Agouzoul (born 10 August 1997) is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a defender for Royal Excel Mouscron, on loan from Lille. ==Club career== A youth product of Kawkab Marrakech, Agouzoul debuted with the first team in 2017. On 11 July 2019, Agouzoul signed a professional contract with Ligue 1 side Lille OSC for five years. ==International career== Agouzoul was called up to a pair of 2019 Africa U-23 Cup of Nations qualification matches for the Morocco U23s in March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Marrakesh Category:Moroccan footballers Category:Morocco youth international footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Lille OSC players Category:Royal Excel Mouscron players Category:Botola players Category:Championnat National 2 players Category:Moroccan expatriate footballers Category:Moroccan expatriate sportspeople in France Category:Expatriate footballers in France
